    <section id="privacy" class="section privacy">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="privacy-content">
                <div class="privacy-header fade-in">
                    <h1 class="section-title">
                        Privacy <span class="gradient-text">Policy</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="privacy-subtitle">
                        Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
                    </p>
                    <div class="last-updated">
                        <span class="updated-label">Last Updated:</span>
                        <span class="updated-date">January 15, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="privacy-body fade-in">
                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Information We Collect</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            We collect information to provide better services to our users and ensure a safe, exclusive experience.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, date of birth, and government-issued ID details for age verification.</li>
                            <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit card details, billing address, and transaction history processed through secure payment providers.</li>
                            <li><strong>Event Information:</strong> Ticket purchases, attendance records, preferences, and special requests.</li>
                            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, and website usage analytics.</li>
                            <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Support inquiries, feedback, and any correspondence with our team.</li>
                            <li><strong>Marketing Preferences:</strong> Subscription status, communication preferences, and engagement data.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">How We Use Your Information</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            Your information helps us deliver exceptional service and maintain our exclusive community standards.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Event Management:</strong> Process ticket purchases, manage guest lists, and facilitate event entry.</li>
                            <li><strong>Age Verification:</strong> Ensure compliance with 21+ age requirements for all events.</li>
                            <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send event updates, confirmations, and important announcements.</li>
                            <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Respond to inquiries, resolve issues, and provide assistance.</li>
                            <li><strong>Security:</strong> Monitor for fraudulent activity and ensure venue safety.</li>
                            <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> Send promotional materials and event invitations (with your consent).</li>
                            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Improve our services, website functionality, and user experience.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Information Sharing</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            We do not sell your personal information. We may share information only in the following circumstances:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Third-party vendors who assist with payment processing, email delivery, and analytics.</li>
                            <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or government regulation.</li>
                            <li><strong>Safety & Security:</strong> To protect the rights, property, or safety of our users, staff, or the public.</li>
                            <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets.</li>
                            <li><strong>Venue Partners:</strong> Limited information sharing with event venues for security and logistics purposes.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="privacy-highlight">
                            <p>We never sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Data Security</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All sensitive data is encrypted during transmission and storage.</li>
                            <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Limited access to personal information on a need-to-know basis.</li>
                            <li><strong>Secure Systems:</strong> Regular security audits and updates to our systems and infrastructure.</li>
                            <li><strong>Payment Security:</strong> PCI DSS compliant payment processing with tokenization.</li>
                            <li><strong>Data Minimization:</strong> We collect only the information necessary for our services.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Your Rights & Choices</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            You have several rights regarding your personal information and how we use it.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal information we hold about you.</li>
                            <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct inaccurate personal information.</li>
                            <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal information (subject to legal requirements).</li>
                            <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format.</li>
                            <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications at any time.</li>
                            <li><strong>Restrict Processing:</strong> Limit how we use your information in certain circumstances.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="contact-info">
                            <p><strong>To exercise these rights, contact us at:</strong></p>
                            <p>Email: privacy@scratchunleashed.com</p>
                            <p>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
                            <p>Response Time: Within 30 days</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Cookies & Tracking</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience and analyze website usage.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for website functionality and security.</li>
                            <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors interact with our website.</li>
                            <li><strong>Marketing Cookies:</strong> Enable personalized advertising and content.</li>
                            <li><strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> Remember your settings and preferences.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            You can control cookies through your browser settings, though this may affect website functionality.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Photography & Media</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            By attending our events, you consent to photography and video recording for promotional purposes.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Event Photography:</strong> Professional photographers may capture images during events.</li>
                            <li><strong>Social Media:</strong> Photos and videos may be used on our social media platforms.</li>
                            <li><strong>Marketing Materials:</strong> Images may appear in future promotional content.</li>
                            <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Contact us if you prefer not to be included in promotional materials.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Changes to This Policy</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. When we do, we will notify you of any material changes.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="privacy-list">
                            <li><strong>Email Notification:</strong> Significant changes will be communicated via email.</li>
                            <li><strong>Website Notice:</strong> Updates will be posted on our website with the revision date.</li>
                            <li><strong>Continued Use:</strong> Using our services after changes indicates acceptance of the updated policy.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="privacy-section">
                        <h2 class="privacy-section-title">Contact Information</h2>
                        <p class="privacy-text">
                            If you have questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us.
                        </p>
                        <div class="contact-info">
                            <p><strong>Privacy Officer</strong></p>
                            <p>Email: privacy@scratchunleashed.com</p>
                            <p>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
                            <p>Mail: Scratch Unleashed Privacy Department<br>
                            123 Nightlife Avenue, Suite 100<br>
                            City, State 12345</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<style>
    :root {
        --primary-gold: #D4AF37;
        --secondary-gold: #F4E4BC;
        --dark-bg: #000000;
        --secondary-dark: #0A0A0A;
        --tertiary-dark: #1A1A1A;
        --text-light: #FFFFFF;
        --text-muted: #A0A0A0;
        --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4AF37 0%, #F4E4BC 100%);
        --gradient-overlay: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2) 0%, rgba(244, 228, 188, 0.1) 100%);
        --shadow-dark: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        --shadow-gold: 0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    }

    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        background: var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--text-light);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .section {
        padding: 100px 0;
    }

    .gradient-text {
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .fade-in {
        animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    .privacy {
        background: var(--dark-bg);
        position: relative;
        min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .privacy::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%),
                    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .privacy-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .privacy-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .privacy-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .last-updated {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: var(--tertiary-dark);
        border: 1px solid var(--primary-gold);
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .updated-label {
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .updated-date {
        color: var(--primary-gold);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .privacy-body {
        margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .privacy-section {
        margin-bottom: 50px;
        padding: 30px;
        background: var(--secondary-dark);
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .privacy-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 4px;
        height: 100%;
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
    }

    .privacy-section-title {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary-gold);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-text {
        color: var(--text-light);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-list li {
        color: var(--text-light);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-list li::before {
        content: 'â€¢';
        color: var(--primary-gold);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
    }

    .privacy-list li strong {
        color: var(--primary-gold);
    }

    .privacy-highlight {
        background: var(--tertiary-dark);
        border: 1px solid var(--primary-gold);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        margin-left: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-highlight p {
        color: var(--primary-gold);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .contact-info {
        background: var(--tertiary-dark);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        margin-left: 20px;
    }

    .contact-info p {
        color: var(--text-light);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .contact-info strong {
        color: var(--primary-gold);
    }

    .privacy-footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--tertiary-dark);
    }

    .footer-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        color: var(--dark-bg);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-gold);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--text-light);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--primary-gold);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: var(--primary-gold);
        color: var(--dark-bg);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section {
            padding: 60px 0;
        }

        .privacy-content {
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .privacy-section {
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .privacy-section-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .privacy-text {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .privacy-list {
            padding-left: 30px;
        }

        .privacy-highlight {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .footer-actions {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .btn-primary,
        .btn-secondary {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .privacy-section {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .privacy-section-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .privacy-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .privacy-list {
            padding-left: 25px;
        }

        .privacy-highlight {
            margin-left: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-left: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
        }
    }
</style>
